Over the weekend we picked up a new pack member! 🐾

Meet Buddy, an 80 pound, velvety soft, sweet Goldendoodle. He is only one year old and still has all of the puppy energy! 🐶🦴 He loves bones, balls, and beds 😂

Mako has always been an only dog and she truly is my soul dog. She didn’t take it very well initially, but she is slowly warming up to Buddy. It broke my heart that she wasn’t fully comfortable with this decision, so we weren’t sure if he was going to stay, but she’s getting more comfortable each day and has taken a liking to him. She is still my baby and my world, that will never change. We just have even more love to give (and receive) in our home 🏡💗

All that said, this week has been extremely hectic. Not only did we pick up this big boy, but we’re moving houses soon so we’ve been packing and cleaning, AND I got the job that I’ve been interviewing for! 😁 while this is all exciting, it’s been a lot! So I apologize in my absence from Instagram this weekend, I’m sure things will go more smoothly now! Until we move at least 😂

Everyone, welcome, BUDDY! 🐾

Whoooooo! 😮‍💨 it’s been a month! 📆

I decided to relax and unwind with @yunasence_beauty products 😶‍🌫️

I started with their Very Berry Organic Oxygen Masque and Scrub 🍓 it’s a two in one exfoliator and masque, making masking and exfoliating easy at the end of a long day (or week). 🧼🫧

Then I tried their Restoring Leave on Lip Mask and OMG 😳 this is my new favourite lip product! I love a lip treatment I can leave on, especially at night before bed. This one is so moisturizing and leaves my lips super soft! 😍

Lastly I gave the Hydrating & Firming Caviar Butter a try on my arms and legs. I love a good lotion 🧴 for my tattoos and love that this one is firming. My dogs also couldn’t get enough of the smell! 🤣

Have you tried @yunasence_beauty yet? What products would you try? 🤔

@thisisbutterly & @benzagelcanada gifted me their Acne Wash, Acne Gel 5% and their Aftercare Moisturizing Lotion in exchange for my review! 😍

I am an adult acne sufferer and have been for the better part of the last decade 😫 I struggle mostly with hormonal acne now, though it is getting better as I get older.

My thoughts 🤔

@benzagelcanada Acne Gel 5% this is a great spot treatment for smaller breakouts that happen throughout the month. I love that it didn’t leave my face feeling tacky after! 

Benzagel Acne Wash this has a great lather and I definitely think it is effective for someone who has less breakouts than me.

@benzagelcanada After Care Moisturizing Lotion - my fave of the bunch! I love the texture of this moisturizer. It’s silky and smooth and super cooling on the skin. I enjoy using it after spending a day out in the sun! 

Do you use Benzagel? Give me your recommendations! 💭
